# Feature Requirements for Doraplexis

## 1. 女生守护者 (Women's Health Tracker)

### Functionality
- Track menstrual cycle with user input of:
  - Last period date
  - Age
  - Typical cycle length
- Display current day in cycle
- Show phase indicators (经期/排卵期/安全期/黄体期)
- Provide countdown to next period
- Display reminders with health tips

### Implementation Details
- Store cycle data using `SharedPreferences`
- Calculate phases based on typical menstrual cycle patterns
- Use notifications for reminders (optional)

## 2. 穿搭消费账单 (Fashion Expense Tracker)

### Functionality
- Track spending on:
  - 服装 (Clothing)
  - 鞋子 (Shoes)
  - 首饰 (Jewelry)
  - 包 (Bags)
- Generate monthly reports
- Display spending trends
- Compare with previous months

### Implementation Details
- Store expense data using `SharedPreferences`
- Use `DateTime` for tracking monthly patterns
- Implement bar charts for visual representation

## 3. 收纳屋 (Storage Organizer)

### Functionality
- Record items with:
  - Name
  - Location (卧室/客厅/厨房/衣帽间/其他)
  - Sub-location (specific storage details)
  - Date added
- Search functionality
- Statistical analysis by location
- Visual representation with pie charts

### Implementation Details
- Store item data using `SharedPreferences`
- Implement search algorithm for finding items
- Create pie chart visualization for item distribution

## General Requirements
- Chinese language UI
- No account/login functionality required
- Dark theme with specified color palette
- Use local storage only (no cloud sync)